summary:
Don\'t expect too much!
Just a mod to increase your jumpheight and movementspeed *2 and turns of fallingdamage.
It\'s just 3 simple Commands in 1 bat , nothing special...
descriptionHtml:
This is my first mod, which I actually just did for myself, because I\'m too lazy to type some commands manually in the console...
so I packed the 3 commands in one.

It doubles your Jumpheight and movementspeed to let you jump higher and further.
It also turns of the fallingdamage for specific heights.

Feel free to play around with the .txt file!

---Install---
Just use NexusModManager
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/modmanager/
or throw the .txt in the Data folder...

---Requirements---
can\'t say there are any...

---Usage---

just open the console and type: bat Acrobatics



Have fun!
author: Blowfish777
